You know I'm gonna be there.

850
01:14:05,647 --> 01:14:07,350
All right, let's go.

851
01:14:13,055 --> 01:14:14,256
We got a signal.

852
01:14:15,257 --> 01:14:17,189
Gally did it.

853
01:14:17,191 --> 01:14:18,293
