side of the building.

880
01:16:21,016 --> 01:16:22,814
Okay, take me to him.
Right now.

881
01:16:22,816 --> 01:16:24,384
All right.
I'm coming with you.

882
01:16:24,386 --> 01:16:25,484
Newt, no, you're not.

883
01:16:25,486 --> 01:16:27,920
